Title: Birthmarks

GuestStars: Diane Baker, R. Lee Ermey, Samantha Quan, Scott Paulin, Christine Healy, Jack Conley, Ho-Kwan Tse, Raymond Ma, Esther Kwan, Jonathan Palmer, Bobbin Bergstrom
